{{Otheruses|Nova crystal}}
The '''Nova Crystal''' looked like a chunk of black [[Glass/Legends|glass]] about the size of a [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee's]] fist. It was not very heavy but felt warm to the touch. Red and blue light would explode deep inside the [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]] every few minutes, which looked very much like a [[Star/Legends|star]] going [[Nova/Legends|nova]] in the depths of [[Realspace/Legends|space]]. It was thought that the crystal could have perhaps been a [[The Force/Legends|Force]] artifact. Many beings were known to have wanted the crystal, [[Gordunga]] and [[Keith]] among them. [[Pothos Fine]] gave his life to protect the crystal from coming into the hands of Keith.

